      <title>Spirit 濒临破产，股东可能破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/spirit-nears-bankruptcy-that-can-wipe-out-equity-holders-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Spirit Airlines Inc. 周二晚间提交的文件显示，该公司即将与债权人达成协议，将在破产法庭上重组其沉重的债务负担，这“预计将导致公司现有股权被取消”。Siddharth Philip 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-13/spirit-nears-bankruptcy-that-can-wipe-out-equity-holders-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 10:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
